      • isTraverse

        protected boolean isTraverse(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent event)
        Returns true if the given KeyEvent should trigger focus traversal. Otherwise returns false. Per default returns true if <Tab> is pressed..
        Parameters:
        event - The KeyEvent in question.
        Returns:
        true if the given KeyEvent should trigger focus traversal, otherwise false.
